<template><div><p><sub>Go back to <RouteLink to="/home.html">Linux Apps Library</RouteLink></sub></p>
<h1 id="gnomie" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#gnomie"><span>Gnomie</span></a></h1>
<h2 id="dconf-editor" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#dconf-editor"><span><a href="https://flathub.org/apps/ca.desrt.dconf-editor" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Dconf Editor</a></span></a></h2>
<p>GUI to edit GSettings/Dconf database (advanced Gnome system settings).</p>
<p><strong>Flatpak (System)</strong></p>
<div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="sh"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line">flatpak <span class="token function">install</span> flathub ca.desrt.dconf-editor</span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>Flatpak (User)</strong></p>
<div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="sh"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line">flatpak <span class="token function">install</span> <span class="token parameter variable">--user</span> flathub ca.desrt.dconf-editor</span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>Disclaimer: If you think that some settings are missing in Dconf, install your distroâ€™s package instead of the Flatpak</strong></p>
<p><strong>Debian/Ubuntu</strong></p>
<div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="sh"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line"><span class="token function">sudo</span> <span class="token function">apt</span> <span class="token function">install</span> dconf-editor</span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>Fedora</strong></p>
<div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="sh"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line"><span class="token function">sudo</span> dnf <span class="token function">install</span> dconf-editor</span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>Arch</strong></p>
<div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="sh"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line"><span class="token function">sudo</span> pacman <span class="token parameter variable">-S</span> dconf-editor</span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="extension-manager" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#extension-manager"><span><a href="https://flathub.org/apps/com.mattjakeman.ExtensionManager" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Extension Manager</a></span></a></h2>
<p>GUI to modify Gnome Extensions.</p>
<p><strong>Flatpak (System)</strong></p>
<div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="sh"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line">flatpak <span class="token function">install</span> flathub com.mattjakeman.ExtensionManager</span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>Flatpak (User)</strong></p>
<div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="sh"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line">flatpak <span class="token function">install</span> <span class="token parameter variable">--user</span> flathub com.mattjakeman.ExtensionManager</span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="gnome-tweaks" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#gnome-tweaks"><span><a href="https://github.com/GNOME/gnome-tweaks" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Gnome Tweaks</a></span></a></h2>
<p>Change fonts, manage shell themes (requires <code v-pre>User Theme</code> extension), add hide and maximize buttons, and more!</p>
<p><strong>Debian/Ubuntu</strong></p>
<div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="sh"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line"><span class="token function">sudo</span> <span class="token function">apt</span> <span class="token function">install</span> gnome-tweaks</span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>Fedora</strong></p>
<div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="sh"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line"><span class="token function">sudo</span> dnf <span class="token function">install</span> gnome-tweaks</span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><h2 id="savedesktop" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#savedesktop"><span><a href="https://flathub.org/apps/io.github.vikdevelop.SaveDesktop" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">SaveDesktop</a></span></a></h2>
<p>Save your desktop configurations</p>
<p><strong>Flatpak (System)</strong></p>
<div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="sh"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line">flatpak <span class="token function">install</span> flathub io.github.vikdevelop.SaveDesktop</span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div><p><strong>Flatpak (User)</strong></p>
<div class="language-bash line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="prismjs" data-ext="sh"><pre v-pre><code><span class="line">flatpak <span class="token function">install</span> flathub io.github.vikdevelop.SaveDesktop</span>
<span class="line"></span></code></pre>
<div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true" style="counter-reset:line-number 0"><div class="line-number"></div></div></div></div></template>


